@host = http://localhost:5204

### 📋 List all available endpoints
GET {{host}}/
Accept: application/json

### ✅ Scenario 1: Valid user — should return 200
POST {{host}}/api/user/valid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "email": "alice@contoso.com",
  "delay": 100
}

### ❌ Scenario 2: Invalid email domain — bob@gmail.com ≠ contoso.com
POST {{host}}/api/user/invalid-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "email": "bob@gmail.com",
  "delay": 100
}

### ❌ Scenario 3: Invalid event — StartDate after EndDate
POST {{host}}/api/event/invalid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Launch Party",
  "startDate": "2026-12-25",
  "endDate": "2026-12-20",
  "delay": 100
}

### ❌ Scenario 4: Order over limit — $100k > $50k
POST {{host}}/api/order/over-limit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Widget",
  "quantity": 10000,
  "unitPrice": 10,
  "delay": 100
}

### ❌ Scenario 5: Invalid profile — "admin" reserved + bio too long
POST {{host}}/api/profile/invalid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "bio": "xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx",
  "delay": 100
}
